content: <?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?> <metadata xml:lang="en"> <Esri> <CreaDate>20140212</CreaDate> <CreaTime>13523800</CreaTime> <ArcGISFormat>1.0</ArcGISFormat> <SyncOnce>TRUE</SyncOnce> </Esri> <dataIdInfo> <idAbs>A dynamic map service showing polygon extents of bathymetric and topographic digital elevation models (DEMs) hosted at NGDC and elsewhere on the web. Layers available in the map service: Layers 1-4: DEMs by Category. Includes various DEMs, both hosted at NGDC, and elsewhere on the web. Layers 6-11: NGDC DEM Projects. DEMs hosted at NGDC, color-coded by project. Layer 12: All NGDC Bathymetry DEMs. All bathymetry or bathy-topo DEMs hosted at NGDC. This service can be viewed in these interactive mapping applications: Bathymetry Data Viewer (http://maps.ngdc.noaa.gov/viewers/bathymetry/) Coastal DEM Search / DEM Discovery Portal (http://ngdc.noaa.gov/dem/squareCellGrid/search) For more information about bathymetry and digital elevation models at NGDC, please see: http://ngdc.noaa.gov/mgg/bathymetry/relief.html Catalog of FGDC metadata for DEMs hosted at NGDC: http://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/metadata/published/NOAA/NESDIS/NGDC/MGG/DEM/fgdc/</idAbs> <searchKeys> <keyword>DEM</keyword> <keyword>digital elevation model</keyword> <keyword>bathymetry</keyword> <keyword>topography</keyword> <keyword>seafloor</keyword> <keyword>oceans</keyword> <keyword>coasts</keyword> <keyword>NGDC</keyword> <keyword>NOAA</keyword> </searchKeys> <idPurp>A map service showing polygon extents of bathymetric and topographic digital elevation models (DEMs) hosted at NGDC, and elsewhere on the web.</idPurp> <idCredit>NOAA Environmental Satelite, Data, & Information Service (NESDIS), National Geophysical Data Center (NGDC)</idCredit> <resConst> <Consts> <useLimit/> </Consts> </resConst> <idCitation> <resTitle>Digital Elevation Model Footprints</resTitle> </idCitation> </dataIdInfo> <Binary> <Thumbnail> <Data EsriPropertyType="PictureX"></Data> </Thumbnail> </Binary> </metadata>
